        <div1 type="summary">
            <p><add hand="#barker">Appoints Austin his deputy in extending titles to settlers.</add></p>
        </div1>
        <div1 type="body">
            

<p>Having been called by the Government to take my seat in the
Deputation of this Province of which I am a Member, I therefore
Authorise <persName>Lieutenant Colonel Stephen F. Austin</persName> to proceed in my<pb n="725"/>
absence with the Surveying and designating the lands and lots for
<persName>Settlers </persName>within his <placeName>Colony </placeName>and to do whatever may be necessary
towards completing the affairs of the <placeName>Colony </placeName>untill my return,
<placeName>St Felipe de Austin</placeName></p>
<p><date when="1824-01-20">January 20- 1824</date></p>

<p><persName>Baron de Bastrop   [Rubric]
Govnt Commissioner</persName> </p>

        </div1>
